        "zh": "1.產品設計過程的講解<br>2.產品、市場與消費者的概述<br>3.消費性產品設計的介紹<br>4.生活產品設計的介紹<br>5.家具設計的介紹<br>6.工藝產品的差異<br>7.使學生熟悉產品設計過程與製作<br>",
        "en": "1.Product Design Process<br>2.Product, Market and Customer<br>3.Customerize Product Design<br>4.Life product design introduction<br>5.Funitrune Design introduction<br>6.Craft Design differencication<br>7.Understanding of product design process and execution<br>"
